ConfigurationOption.Value: select wo.wonum, wo.description, wo.status, wo.assetnum, wo.location, wo.workorderid, wo.siteid, lbl.laborcode, lbl.lbl_labtransid, wo.glaccount from workorder wo left outer join lbl_labtrans lbl on lbl.refwo = wo.wonum where wo.historyflag = 0 and wo.istask = 0 and wo.status not in ( 'CAN', 'CLOSE', 'HISTEDIT' ) and lbl.lbl_status = 'ASSIGN' and lbl.lbl_transtype = 'PLAN'
